readValue

public IndicatorType readValue(java.io.DataInput input,
                               int dataSize)
                        throws java.io.IOException
Reads a field value of this type from a DataInput source. This method must be overridden by any custom types. The implementation must read exactly the number of bytes passed as dataSize.
